.TH SHIPFORGE 1 "2026-06-29" "DevCore 0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
shipforge \- generate structured change receipts for AI-generated code
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B shipforge
.RI [ COMMAND ]
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B init
Initialize ShipForge in the current project.
.TP
.B receipt [\-c OID]
Generate a change receipt for HEAD or a specific commit.
.TP
.B log [\-n LIMIT] [\-\-ai\-only]
List recent change receipts.
.TP
.B show OID [\-f FORMAT]
Display a stored change receipt.
.TP
.B explain FILE
Show why a file exists and what depends on it.
.TP
.B blast FILE
Show blast radius for a file change.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I .devcore/devcore.db
SQLite database storing change receipts.
.TP
.I .devcore/config.toml
Project configuration (optional).
.SH SEE ALSO
codetrail(1), devpulse(1)
